profile:
Integrity Builders Ltd has been building quality homes, renovations and additions in the Victoria area since 2004. Projects have included custom homes, basement renovations, kitchen and Bath remodels, commercial kitchens, as well as several group homes. No project is too big or too small. Integrity Builders is a licensed builder registered with the Home Owner Protection office and can provide new home warranty coverage through Travelers Canada.

We’re thrilled that you’re considering us for your renovations and additions! With Integrity Builders, no project is too difficult to complete. We enjoy the challenges we might face and we strive to give you the best results possible.

Are you ready to complete the renovations and additions you’ve always wanted? Integrity Builders is ready to help you make those dreams come true! Contact us today to get started on improving your house to finally reach the perfect home you’ve been waiting for.
services:
New Home Construction
Major Renovations 
Additions
Kitchen and Bath renovations

profile:
We build , renovate and repair . 
Passion, quality work, and professionalism is what New Mount Homes lives by.
At the age of fifteen I had started my first renovation project. I completely remodeled my parent’s bathroom, kitchen and went on to install hardwood flooring for them.

Talent comes naturally to all of us, skill is only developed by hours and hours of working on your craft. We take great pride in every project that’s completed. Quality craftsmanship is our standard.

We work very closely with our clients to achieve their vision. Reinvigorating the familiar, NewMount Homes creates a space that is totally new but still completely yours.

With our decades of experience, cutting-edge building practices and our renowned attention to detail, renovating your home with NewMount Homes brings peace of mind, great customer service and top-notch style.

Our Flexibility in design allows us to work within any budget. Whether your idea of luxury is traditional, modern or a combination of styles we can help!

It’s Time – Let NewMount Homes show you what your Home could be!
